Class TypedProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Dictionary<K,V>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object>

    public class TypedProperties
extends java.util.Properties
    This class provides typed access to attributes in java.util.Properties. Extends java.util.Properties and implements variations of getProperty() method for accessing boolean, int, long, double and of course String values.
    See Also:

        public static final java.lang.String SERIALIZATION_CHARSET_NAME
